ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺好微妙"},{"pid":"d3b3cafaae3d72c45aaba4010838d11d55d6d1b3","tid":518304,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dcd7cf453cd7bf54ea5bc24b24490bb9e7e59a25","tid":518304,"uid":45749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:21:42.000Z","msg":"我老豆都好仆街<br />\n不過佢死之前幾年老人痴呆得好嚴重<br />\n佢嘅思維返左三十幾年前<br />\n果時我未出世但我家姐出左世<br />\n佢就同我傾返佢老豆佢個女啲野<br />\n明明都係我識嘅人，但佢就當我係新朋友咁介紹家人畀我識。<br />\n<br />\n我真嘅老豆就當係佢病發前已死左<br />\n而我去幫佢披麻嘅，就好似係另一位識左幾年朋友咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺好微妙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我其實唔係好相信死者為大同埋死前認錯<br />\n唔知係咪算冷血,但我覺得一個人肯認錯係太容易既事"},{"pid":"69fd1285c4ac5c6297bf23ac3c0dc70ef2152777","tid":518304,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d509125760185d7c94d6555739c7d0602589d98c","tid":518304,"uid":15945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69fd1285c4ac5c6297bf23ac3c0dc70ef2152777","tid":518304,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:43:58.000Z","msg":"樓主自己咪在生果個囉<br />\n披麻戴孝令佢好唔開心喎"},{"pid":"4cc212ddc08a36f3671ce1270cab4948adb184cb","tid":518304,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d509125760185d7c94d6555739c7d0602589d98c","tid":518304,"uid":15945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69fd1285c4ac5c6297bf23ac3c0dc70ef2152777","tid":518304,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:43:58.000Z","msg":"樓主自己咪在生果個囉<br />\n披麻戴孝令佢好唔開心喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi